No. 220,

Misc.

Smith v. Texas. J. E. Winjree, Jr. for petitioner. Will Wilson, Attorney General of Texas, and Sam B. Wilson and Houghton Brownlee, Jr., Assistant Attorneys General, for respondent.

Court of Criminal Appeals of Texas. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion certiorari should be granted.
